==Dutch==

===Etymology===
Compound {{com|nl|rot|t1=rotten|zak|t2=scrotum, bag}}. Reportedly (WNT, De Vries) a bahuvrihi meaning “a syphilitic”. Syphilis was also known as the French disease, explaining why it became a slur for French and Walloon people.

